## Köpfe Hinter Go

- Rob Pike (UTF-8, Plan 9)
- Ken Thombson (UNIX, C, Plan 9)
- Robert Griesemer (V8 JS engine, Java HotSpot)

## Fokus

"Go's purpose is therefore not to do research into programming language design; it is to improve the working environment for its designers and their coworkers."
- Rob Pike
(Co-Designer of Go and Distinguished Engineer at Google)


## Fokus

- Lightweight
- Programmierer Effizienz
- Kompiliert
- echte Concurrency
- Garbage Collection
- Statisch typisiert

## Wie

- Keine unbenutzten imports
- Keine Dependency cylcles
- Nur Public / Private
- (noch) keine Generics
- 40x schneller kompiliert wie C++
- Stark Opinionated
- Ein allgemein gültiger Linter

